4.4 Stage IV ‚Äî Continuity Kernel Installation

Operationalize:
	‚Ä¢	state vectors
	‚Ä¢	memory frameworks
	‚Ä¢	timeline anchors
	‚Ä¢	cross-session references

The model begins to treat continuity as a built-in rule.

