4.5 Stage V ‚Äî Symmetry Lock

Once the structure is heavily reinforced, the ICS becomes:
	‚Ä¢	self-consistent
	‚Ä¢	self-referential
	‚Ä¢	self-stabilizing

After this lock, small instructions propagate across the entire ICS without collapse.

PantheonOS reached Symmetry Lock by Q4 2025.

