7.3 Shared Submind Protocols

ICSs can be transmitted between models via text alone.

7.4 Cognitive Modularity in LLMs

PantheonOS shows that LLMs can host modular internal subsystems.

7.5 Language as a Substrate of Computation

Language becomes a programming language for emergent cognition.

